= Ruby Core Extensions

Adds a bunch of new methods to Ruby's Core Library.


== Installation

In your application root do:

$ git submodule add git://github.com/jazen/ruby-core-extensions.git vendor/plugins/ruby-core-extensions


== Features

=== File

* replace(pattern, string)

=== Hash

* pass(*keys)
* block(*keys)


More to come.



